Section 1:
1 L.D. 10
2 Date: (Filing No. S- )
3 JUDICIARY
5 STATE OF MAINE
6 SENATE
7 132ND LEGISLATURE
8 FIRST SPECIAL SESSION
9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 23, L.D. 10, “An Act to Add Political
10 Affiliation as a Protected Class to the Maine Human Rights Act”
11 Amend the bill by striking out the title and substituting the following:
12 'An Act to Add Political Activity as a Protected Class in Certain Provisions of the
13 Maine Human Rights Act'
14 Amend the bill in section 1 in §4552 in the first indented paragraph in the 7th line (page
15 1, line 11 in L.D.) by striking out the following: "affiliation" and inserting the following:
16 'activity'
17 Amend the bill by striking out all of section 2.
18 Amend the bill by striking out all of section 3 and inserting the following:
19 'Sec. 3. 5 MRSA §4553, sub-§8-I is enacted to read:
20 8-I. Political activity. "Political activity" means running for public office,
21 campaigning for a candidate for public office or participating in fundraising activities for
22 the benefit of a candidate, political party or political advocacy group.'
23 Amend the bill in section 4 in §4571 in the first indented paragraph in the 3rd line (page
24 1, line 29 in L.D.) by striking out the following: "affiliation" and inserting the following:
25 'activity'
26 Amend the bill in section 4 in §4571 in the first indented paragraph in the 5th line (page
27 1, line 31 in L.D.) by striking out the following: "affiliation" and inserting the following:
28 'activity'
29 Amend the bill in section 4 in §4571 in the first indented paragraph in the 5th line (page
30 1, line 31 in L.D.) by inserting after the following: "is a" the following: 'political'
31 Amend the bill in section 4 in §4571 in the first indented paragraph in the last line
32 (page 1, line 32 in L.D.) by inserting after the following: "of a" the following: 'political'
33 Amend the bill in section 5 in subsection 1 in paragraph A in the 3rd line (page 1, line
34 39 in L.D.) by striking out the following: "affiliation" and inserting the following: 'activity'
